<span id="freeTextContainer14374551837067162044">Blake Butler is the author of EVER, Scorch Atlas, and two books forthcoming in 2011 and 2012 from Harper Perennial. He edits &apos;the internet literature magazine blog of the future&apos; HTML Giant. His other writing have appeared in The Believer, Unsaid, Fence, Dzanc&apos;s Best of the Web 2009. He lives in Atlanta.</span>
